ICE lodged an "arrest detainer" for Aristides Eli Orellana-Ramirez, an illegal alien from El Salvador charged with murdering two teenagers in Charlotte, according to DHS. (Department of Homeland Security)

In a harrowing detail, investigators said the [victims’ bodies](https://www.foxnews.com/category/us/crime/homicide) were found more than 6 miles apart. Detectives believe the teens were "shot at the same location during the same incident and then traveled away from the scene in an attempt to find help."

While the investigation remains ongoing, the case has already become a [political lightning rod](https://www.foxnews.com/category/controversies).

According to DHS, Orellana-Ramirez entered the U.S. illegally at an unknown date and location without inspection.

